{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"236","heading":"Personal protection equipment procurement: display of budget information","label":"236 Personal protection equipment procurement: display of budget information","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptI/ch9","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Budget Justification Display","label":"a .—Budget Justification Display","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of Defense shall submit to Congress, as a part of the defense budget materials for each fiscal year after fiscal year 2014, a consolidated budget justification display that covers all programs and activities associated with the procurement of personal protection equipment during the period covered by the future-years defense program submitted in that fiscal year under section 221.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Requirements for Budget Display","label":"b .—Requirements for Budget Display","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The amount for personal protection equipment included in both the base budget of the President and any overseas contingency operations budget of the President.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A brief description of each category of personal protection equipment for each military department planned to be procured and developed.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the relevant appropriations account, budget activity, and subactivity group for the category; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the funding profile for the fiscal year as requested, including cost and quantities, and an estimate of projected investments or procurements for each of the subsequent five fiscal years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the relevant appropriations account, program, project or activity; program element number, and line number; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/b/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fb%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the funding profile for the fiscal year as requested and an estimate of projected investments for each of the subsequent five fiscal years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":".—Definitions","label":"c .—Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s236/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs236%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The 